{"tid":842931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：疑似中共女子在英國保守黨香港座談會打人！","createTime":"2018-09-30T16:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T17:01:12.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d071ad6208a949b4c7613dc4c63e18f3536af06","tid":842931,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/09/ccp-uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F09%2Fccp-uk%2F&d=NFQt358hQrnvUw6KPkXYQC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6a0c4e3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/09/ccp-uk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180930165241im_/http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/CCP-woman-UK-Conference.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20180930165241im_%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2FCCP-woman-UK-Conference.jpg&h=10eab6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會主席菲安娜.布魯斯Fiona Bruce今日在保守黨會議室主持座談會，題目係香港自由自治受損，講者包括香港監察主席羅傑斯Benedict Rogers、羅冠聰、李柱銘、戴耀廷，超過八十人出席，答問環節過後，香港時間約九點半，羅傑斯正在總結，「我支持中國，我想中國同中國人成功。」誰料一名中國女子突然企起身發爛渣，向羅傑斯尖叫：「你講大話！你反中！你想分裂中國？你連中國人都不是，其他的則全部係漢奸!」 BRUCE議員乃請她走，但該名中國女子拒絕離去，香港監察一位義工ENOCH（香港留學生）走向該名中國女子，話其必須離開，其拒絕，跟住摑了ENOCH兩巴，警察來到，將該名中國女子拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉該中國女子持記者證入場，但未知其公司名。一有最新消息再報。"},{"pid":"07e4e0778c3e4def3a9b090e5ade31a243ff21a6","tid":842931,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}